Sexual Activity in Risk Behavior Survey

Source: R/sex.R
sex.Rd

Information on sexual activities from the (RBS)

Usage

data(sex)

Format

A tibble with 3,299 rows and 40 variables:

who
Type:integer
Description:Patient ID
txx_prt
Type:factor (First/Reference level = 0)
Description:Total sex partners:
  • 0 = 0
  • 1 = 1
  • 2 = more than one
Levels:0, 1, 2
txx_mprt
Type:factor (First/Reference level = 0)
Description:Total male sex partners:
  • 0 = 0
  • 1 = 1
  • 2 = more than one
Levels:0, 1, 2
txx_fprt
Type:factor (First/Reference level = 0)
Description:Total female sex partners:
  • 0 = 0
  • 1 = 1
  • 2 = more than one
Levels:0, 1, 2
msw_npt
Type:factor (First/Reference level = 0)
Description:Men who have sex with women (MSW), sex partners:
  • 0 = 0
  • 1 = 1
  • 2 = more than one
Levels:0, 1, 2
msw_frq
Type:integer
Description:MSW count of sex
msw_pxx
Type:integer
Description:MSW count of protected (with condom use) sex
msw_uxx
Type:integer
Description:MSW count of unprotected sex
msm_npt
Type:factor (First/Reference level = 0)
Description:Men have sex with men (MSM), sex partners:
  • 0 = 0
  • 1 = 1
  • 2 = more than one
Levels:0, 1, 2
msm_frq
Type:integer
Description:MSM count of sex
msm_pxx
Type:integer
Description:MSM count of protected (with condom use) sex
msm_uxx
Type:integer
Description:MSM count of unprotected sex
wsm_npt
Type:factor (First/Reference level = 0)
Description:Women have sex with men (WSM), sex partners:
  • 0 = 0
  • 1 = 1
  • 2 = more than one
Levels:0, 1, 2
wsm_frq
Type:integer
Description:WSM count of sex
wsm_pxx
Type:integer
Description:WSM count of protected (with condom use) sex
wsm_uxx
Type:integer
Description:WSM count of unprotected sex
txx_frq
Type:integer
Description:TOTAL count of sex
txx_pxx
Type:integer
Description:TOTAL count of protected (with condom use) sex
txx_uxx
Type:integer
Description:TOTAL count of unprotected sex
mvw_frq
Type:integer
Description:Men vaginal sex with women count of sex
maw_frq
Type:integer
Description:Men anal sex with women count of sex
mim_frq
Type:integer
Description:Men insertive sex with men count of sex

Type:integer
Description:Men receptive sex with men count of sex
wvm_frq
Type:integer
Description:Women vaginal sex with men count of sex
wam_frq
Type:integer
Description:Women anal sex with men count of sex

Type:integer
Description:Men vaginal sex with women count of protected sex
